{"tid":2134212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【全面宣戰】全囯進入準戰狀態，中囯一招可擊敗美國！","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T14:59:13.000Z","uid":191338,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"744678b3a2cb1cc1fcf0c932212611929053236e","tid":2134212,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"【我愛囯安法】<br />\n<br />\n當年日本偷襲珍珠港，搶佔先機<br />\n引發第二次世界大戰<br />\n雖然結果係慘敗，但雖敗猶榮<br />\n<br />\n今日我地為祖國出謀獻策<br />\n打倒美帝，犯我中華者必誅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sOwjd2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsOwjd2W.jpg&h=3ccc769e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼寧號搵囯師擇個風水吉日良辰<br />\n穿過菲律賓南海，可以經新加玻/印尼海峽<br />\n避開五眼聯盟澳紐嘅航道<br />\n橫跨印度洋<br />\n再係同盟囯南非休整補給<br />\n由南太平洋一路向北駛入北太平洋<br />\n目標係美國嘅四大核電廠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQbjd3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQbjd3x.jpg&h=2a06ffbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一丈功成萬骨枯<br />\n食大豆定食樹皮靠呢鋪！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83e2a9c0627b129c1cd83d243365799a4cfe17c","tid":2134212,"uid":226466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"不如打哂東南亞 ， 重組大東亞共榮圈， 打埋澳紐日韓"},{"pid":"a57403850d7631ea56061ebba865397626b897ce","tid":2134212,"uid":191338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e83e2a9c0627b129c1cd83d243365799a4cfe17c","tid":2134212,"uid":226466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"不如打哂東南亞 ， 重組大東亞共榮圈， 打埋澳紐日韓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"澳紐冇咩戰力，不足為懼<br />\n打倒美帝其他諸侯國自然會跪含<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDq4qgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDq4qgX.jpg&h=a39d27b0&s={SIZE}\" />"}